    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Buildings that house clinics specializing in outpatient treatment, including counseling and the dispensing of medication, for relatively mild or controllable mental illness that does not require overnight admittance.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
